  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install hunspell by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --disable-static \
            --with-ui \
            --with-readline &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <sect3>
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <parameter>--with-ui</parameter>: This switch enables Curses terminal
        user interface.
      </para>

      <para>
        <parameter>--with-readline</parameter>: This switch enables Readline
        support for command input editing.
      </para>

    </sect3>

